*keychain-2.4.2.1 (18 Nov 2004)

  18 Nov 2004; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> -keychain-2.4.2.1.ebuild,
  +keychain-2.4.3.ebuild:
  Update to 2.4.3 which fixes ps issues on BSD

